      "role": "user",
      "content": "wow, okay. so you're saying the \"boost\" to the economy is basically a myth? sounds pretty definitive. i guess if you're looking at it from a pure business survival standpoint, the argument for raising it just seems weak. is there really any legitimate economic case for it, or is it mostly just political messaging?",
